# Network Visualisation - Basic






::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
library(igraph)

grime_edge_list <- read.csv(file.choose(), header = TRUE)

grime_08 <- graph_from_data_frame(d= grime_edge_list, directed = TRUE)
plot(grime_08)
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](Basic-Visualisation_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-1-1.png){width=672}
:::

```{.r .cell-code}
grime_08_clean <- delete.edges(grime_08, E(grime_08)[which_loop(grime_08)])

plot(grime_08_clean)
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](Basic-Visualisation_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-1-2.png){width=672}
:::
:::






## Layout

Random






::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
plot(grime_08_clean, layout = layout.random)
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](Basic-Visualisation_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-2-1.png){width=672}
:::
:::






Grid






::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
plot(grime_08_clean, layout = layout.grid)
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](Basic-Visualisation_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-3-1.png){width=672}
:::
:::






Small world/Circle






::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
plot(grime_08_clean, layout = layout.circle)
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](Basic-Visualisation_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-4-1.png){width=672}
:::
:::






Layout by algorithms to demonstrate the relationships a bit better






::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
plot(grime_08_clean, layout = layout_with_dh(grime_08_clean))
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](Basic-Visualisation_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-5-1.png){width=672}
:::

```{.r .cell-code}
plot(grime_08_clean, layout = layout_with_fr(grime_08_clean))
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](Basic-Visualisation_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-5-2.png){width=672}
:::

```{.r .cell-code}
plot(grime_08_clean, layout = layout_with_kk(grime_08_clean))
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](Basic-Visualisation_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-5-3.png){width=672}
:::
:::






## Changing colours of the graph

Vertex colours with verterx.color()






::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
plot(grime_08_clean, vertex.color = "pink")
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](Basic-Visualisation_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-6-1.png){width=672}
:::
:::






Edge colour with edge.color()






::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
plot(grime_08_clean, edge.color = "pink")
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](Basic-Visualisation_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-7-1.png){width=672}
:::
:::






## Changing the Sizes

Edge and vertex size






::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
plot(grime_08_clean, vertex.size = 5, edge.arrow.size = 0.5)
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](Basic-Visualisation_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-8-1.png){width=672}
:::
:::






Edge thickness






::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
plot(grime_08_clean, vertex.size = 5, edge.width = 10)
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](Basic-Visualisation_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-9-1.png){width=672}
:::
:::






## Titles

Main Title






::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
plot(grime_08_clean, vertex.size = 5, edge.arrow.size = 0.5, main = "Grime Collaborations 2008")
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](Basic-Visualisation_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-10-1.png){width=672}
:::
:::






Sub title






::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
plot(grime_08_clean, vertex.size = 5, edge.arrow.size = 0.5, main = "Grime Collaborations", sub = "2008")
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](Basic-Visualisation_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-11-1.png){width=672}
:::
:::






## Labels

Toggle






::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
plot(grime_08_clean, vertex.label = NA)
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](Basic-Visualisation_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-12-1.png){width=672}
:::
:::






Size and Offset






::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
plot(grime_08_clean, vertex.label.cex = 0.5, vertex.label.dist = 2)
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](Basic-Visualisation_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-13-1.png){width=672}
:::
:::






## General considerations for visualizations

Changing the aspect ratio by changing the margings of the plot window.






::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
plot(grime_08_clean, vertex.label = NA)
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](Basic-Visualisation_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-14-1.png){width=672}
:::

```{.r .cell-code}
par(mar =c(0,0,0,0))
plot(grime_08_clean, vertex.label = NA)
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](Basic-Visualisation_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-14-2.png){width=672}
:::
:::






We have reduced the margins all down to zero.

Set a seed to replicate the same layout every time






::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
par(mar =c(0,0,0,0))
set.seed(123)
plot(grime_08_clean, vertex.label = NA)
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](Basic-Visualisation_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-15-1.png){width=672}
:::
:::

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
par(mar =c(0,0,0,0))
set.seed(123)
plot(grime_08_clean, vertex.label = NA)
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](Basic-Visualisation_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-16-1.png){width=672}
:::
:::






The layout is replicated - useful for recreating visuals you use.

## Plotting visuals next to each other

Vertical






::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
par(mfrow = c(2, 1))
par(mar =c(0,0,0,0))
set.seed(123)
plot(grime_08_clean, vertex.label = NA)
set.seed(123)
par(mar =c(0,0,0,0))
plot(grime_08_clean, vertex.label = NA, vertex.size = degree(grime_08_clean))
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](Basic-Visualisation_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-17-1.png){width=672}
:::
:::






Horizontal






::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
par(mfrow = c(1, 2))
set.seed(123)
par(mar =c(0,0,0,0))
plot(grime_08_clean, vertex.label = NA)
set.seed(123)
par(mar =c(0,0,0,0))
plot(grime_08_clean, vertex.label = NA, vertex.size = degree(grime_08_clean))
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](Basic-Visualisation_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-18-1.png){width=672}
:::
:::
